[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]Vamos a actualizar la PCB.
[ENGLISH]Let&#39s update the PCB.
[END_LIST]
[IMG]23.png

[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]Hay un error porque los componentes están bloqueados (<b>locked</b>) en la PCB.
[ENGLISH]There is an error because the components are <b>locked</b> on the PCB.
[END_LIST]
[IMG]24.png

[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]Selecciona la opción <b>Re-associate footprints by reference</b> y haz clic en el botón <b>Update PCB</b>
[ENGLISH]Select the <b>Re-associate footprints by reference</b> option and click the <b>Update PCB</b> button
[END_LIST]
[IMG]25.png

[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]Ahora ya no hay errores.
[ENGLISH]Now there are no errors.
[END_LIST]
[IMG]26.png
[BLOCK_END]

[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
